      <title>中国工业增长是经济复苏的最新迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/china-s-industrial-upswing-is-latest-sign-of-economic-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国制造业活动在三月份出现反弹，结束了连续五个月的下滑，并进一步证明该国工业部门正在为经济复苏建立动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/china-s-industrial-upswing-is-latest-sign-of-economic-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 09:11:01 GMT</pubDate>
